             was indicted for <rs id="t17840707-19-off100" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840707-19-off100" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17840707-19-off100" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17840707-19-cd101" type="crimeDate">24th of June</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840707-19-off100 t17840707-19-cd101"></join> last, one tin cannister, value 2 s. eleven pounds of singlo tea, value 3 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840707-19-victim261" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Jerman
                        <interp inst="t17840707-19-victim261" type="surname" value="Jerman"></interp>
